data.description:
Welcome to your exclusive retreat in this gated community! Agents, please present your business card to security for seamless access to this stunning property that awaits. Step into luxury with new carpets, freshly painted interiors, and recessed lighting. The 42' cabinets and fireplace add elegance, while the gas heating ensures year-round comfort.

The primary bath is a spa-like escape, featuring a separate shower and soaker tub. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a one-car garage, this home offers both space and convenience. Details like chair/crown moulding make this property a true gem.

Don't miss the chance to call this gated community home.

LEASE TERMS: 24-36 MONTHS
SMOKING: NO
PETS: YES - CASE BY CASE BASIS
DEPOSITS: ONE MONTH RENT + PET DEPOSIT $1000 (IF WITH PET/S)
